en_132222_0	Chairman of Lanka Vehicle Importers' Association- Sampath Merenchige says that the prices of imported vehicle would be increased due to the currency fluctuation of Japanese Yen.
en_132222_1	This will result a price increase in imported hybrid cars from 100,000 rupees to 200,000.
en_132222_2	He further noted that VAT increase has no relation to the vehicle price escalation.
